OL,3,CResidents 'appalled' as boil water
OL,4,Cnotice remains a month after parasite
OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FResidents in Brixham say they are
OL,8,Ffrustrated and appalled that they are
OL,9,Fstill having to boil their water, four
OL,10,Fweeks after the water supply was
OL,11,Fcontaminated.
OL,13,FIn May, around 17,000 customers were
OL,14,Fadvised to boil their water after an
OL,15,Foutbreak of the waterborne parasite
OL,16,Fcryptosporidium which causes vomiting
OL,17,Fand diarrhoea.
