OL,7,FWhile work is underway to clean the
OL,8,Fsupply, around 2,500 properties in
OL,9,FHillhead, Kingswear and the upper
OL,10,Fparts of Brixham remain affected by
OL,11,FSouth West Water's boil water notice.
OL,13,FThe company said the source of the
OL,14,Fparasite outbreak has been traced to a
OL,15,Fdamaged valve on a reservoir, and it
OL,16,Fis working "day and night" to clean
OL,17,Fthe network.
