OL,7,FThere have been 100 confirmed cases of
OL,8,Fdiarrhoea and vomiting since the
OL,9,Foutbreak began according to the latest
OL,10,FUK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,11,Ffigures.
OL,13,FBrixham resident Michaela Lewis said
OL,14,Fshe still has symptoms of
OL,15,Fcryptosporidiosis, after first
OL,16,Fbecoming ill at the start of May.
OL,18,FShe said it's "appalling" that the
OL,19,Fissue still hasn't been fixed.
