OL,7,F"It's just not good enough," she said.
OL,8,F"We pay a premium for fresh water and
OL,9,Fwe can't use it. It's unacceptable."
OL,11,F"They're not communicating what's
OL,12,Factually going on or how long this
OL,13,Fcould take, and it feels like there is
OL,14,Fno end in sight," she added.
OL,16,FElaine Lee said the boil water notice
OL,17,Fhas "gone on long enough."
