OL,7,F"They need to sort it out one way or
OL,8,Fthe other," she said. "I know we've
OL,9,Fhad compensation, but we're boiling
OL,10,Fthe kettle non-stop. I'm waiting for
OL,11,Fit to explode."
OL,13,FSian Thomas, who works at a local
OL,14,Fcafe, said it is "ridiculous" that the
OL,15,Fissue still hasn't been fixed.
OL,17,F"We make coffee, so we have to rinse
OL,18,Fthe jugs out after every use and we're
OL,19,Fhaving to rely on bottled water to do
OL,20,Fthat," she explained. "It's just an
OL,21,Fabsolute nightmare."
