OL,7,FIn a statement South West Water, said:
OL,8,F"Our interventions are working, but
OL,9,Fthis is taking time for which we are
OL,10,Fvery sorry.
OL,12,F"We will continue to provide bottled
OL,13,Fwater and support to all our
OL,14,Fcustomers, visitors and businesses
OL,15,Fimpacted by this situation."
OL,17,FSouth West Water is asking people to
OL,18,Fcontinue to use water around their
OL,19,Fhomes for washing, cleaning and
OL,20,Fflushing toilets.
