OL,7,F"Please keep using your water supply
OL,8,Fas usual for bathing, flushing the
OL,9,Ftoilet and laundry," they added.
OL,11,F"This will keep the water circulating
OL,12,Fthrough household pipes aiding in the
OL,13,Foverall flushing process and will help
OL,14,Fto clean property networks."
